<div class="col0 floatLeft firstCol">
<span class="label">Research</span>
<h2>On Specifying for Trustworthiness</h2>
<h6 class="subheader"></h6>
</div>
<hr class="dotted" />
<div id="articleFullText" class="col1 floatLeft firstCol">
<span class="byline">
By Dhaminda B. Abeywickrama, Amel Bennaceur, Greg Chance, Yiannis Demiris, Anastasia Kordoni, Mark Levine, Luke Moffat, Luc Moreau, Mohammad Reza Mousavi, Bashar Nuseibeh, Subramanian Ramamoorthy, Jan Oliver Ringert, James Wilson, Shane Windsor, Kerstin Eder
<br/>
Communications of the ACM,
January 2024,
Vol. 67 No. 1, Pages 98-109<br/>
10.1145/3624699<br/>
<a href="#comments">Comments</a>
</span>
